1
00:01:01,719 --> 00:01:03,119
With immense strength

2
00:01:03,520 --> 00:01:05,000
guarding the immortal gate

3
00:01:05,760 --> 00:01:08,400
Even if all heaven's soldiers fall

4
00:01:09,120 --> 00:01:10,519
I'd still dare alone

5
00:01:11,599 --> 00:01:13,719
to fight the Great Sage

6
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:19,200
Mighty Spirit Power!

7
00:01:20,959 --> 00:01:24,159
The Mighty Spirit dares fight the Great Sage!

8
00:01:24,760 --> 00:01:29,400
What do I, Zhao Qiansun, have to fear from you?

9
00:01:41,799 --> 00:01:42,799
Is my aura

10
00:01:43,719 --> 00:01:44,760
really that strong?

11
00:01:45,879 --> 00:01:47,519
But I haven't even gone all out yet!

12
00:01:49,120 --> 00:01:50,879
I've failed Tianhuo City.

13
00:01:52,200 --> 00:01:53,200
I've lost.

14
00:01:54,400 --> 00:01:55,959
You really are strong.

15
00:01:56,480 --> 00:01:58,079
No, don't be discouraged.

16
00:01:58,239 --> 00:01:59,519
Actually, you're...

17
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,400
you're actually pretty strong too.

18
00:02:02,200 --> 00:02:03,920
Kid, how did you even win?

19
00:02:07,200 --> 00:02:08,520
Impressive!

20
00:02:12,039 --> 00:02:12,840
Su Yang.

21
00:02:13,560 --> 00:02:15,599
Do you have some dirt

22
00:02:15,599 --> 00:02:16,599
on these Black Street guys?

23
00:02:16,719 --> 00:02:18,120
They're trying way too hard.

24
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:20,520
Su Yang.

25
00:02:21,919 --> 00:02:23,000
I'm talking to you.

26
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,039
Again.

27
00:02:33,400 --> 00:02:34,240
Next up.

28
00:02:36,120 --> 00:02:38,080
Truly a contestant from Shanhai City.

29
00:02:38,080 --> 00:02:39,319
Such a calm demeanor

30
00:02:39,319 --> 00:02:40,759
is simply admirable.

31
00:02:40,759 --> 00:02:41,360
We're done for.

32
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,560
This kid's putting on an act.

33
00:02:44,520 --> 00:02:46,199
He'll blow his cover sooner or later.

34
00:02:47,479 --> 00:02:48,280
Call him back.

35
00:02:52,120 --> 00:02:52,879
I see.

36
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:54,240
In a bit,

37
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,840
I'll send you out.

38
00:02:59,639 --> 00:03:00,599
Don't disappoint me.

39
00:03:04,560 --> 00:03:05,319
Why?

40
00:03:05,479 --> 00:03:07,319
I could wipe out their whole team.

41
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:08,800
I believe

42
00:03:09,159 --> 00:03:12,000
you have the power to sweep the field.

43
00:03:12,039 --> 00:03:13,879
But shouldn't you give the others

44
00:03:13,879 --> 00:03:15,319
a chance in the arena too?

45
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:17,319
Fair enough.

46
00:03:22,599 --> 00:03:23,560
Go on. Go get some experience.

47
00:03:23,560 --> 00:03:24,159
Go.

48
00:03:25,879 --> 00:03:28,080
Next up for Tianhuo City is Wang Qiang.

49
00:03:28,520 --> 00:03:30,280
Shanhai City's next contestant

50
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:32,120
is an adorable girl.

51
00:03:32,319 --> 00:03:33,000
That's right.

52
00:03:33,120 --> 00:03:34,520
Her name is Zhong Jun.

53
00:03:38,400 --> 00:03:40,319
Congrats to Zhong Jun on her total victory!

54
00:03:40,439 --> 00:03:41,759
Indeed. Meanwhile,

55
00:03:41,759 --> 00:03:42,680
Tianhuo City has sent out

56
00:03:42,680 --> 00:03:44,240
their third contestant.

57
00:03:44,240 --> 00:03:45,080
As we can see,

58
00:03:45,080 --> 00:03:46,080
on Shanhai City's side,

59
00:03:46,080 --> 00:03:47,879
Zhong Jun is still taking the challenge.

60
00:03:51,479 --> 00:03:52,159
Beautiful!

61
00:03:52,319 --> 00:03:53,800
Zhong Jun has defeated her opponent again.

62
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:56,319
Let's congratulate Zhong Jun on two wins in a row!

63
00:03:58,479 --> 00:03:59,360
Oh my goodness!

64
00:03:59,599 --> 00:04:00,520
Defeated three in a row!

65
00:04:00,719 --> 00:04:01,680
Looks like we can bring out

66
00:04:01,680 --> 00:04:03,319
Tianhuo City's fifth member.

67
00:04:03,759 --> 00:04:04,560
I forfeit.

68
00:04:04,560 --> 00:04:05,159
What?

69
00:04:05,439 --> 00:04:06,759
Tianhuo City's fifth member

70
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:08,000
has actually chosen to forfeit!

71
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,919
He didn't even dare to step on stage!

72
00:04:10,240 --> 00:04:12,879
Truly one of the eight main cities, Shanhai City!

73
00:04:13,199 --> 00:04:14,599
Their strength is indeed formidable!

74
00:04:14,759 --> 00:04:16,959
So let's congratulate Shanhai City!

75
00:04:17,319 --> 00:04:19,720
Next, please enjoy a cheerleading performance.

76
00:04:19,720 --> 00:04:20,439
After the performance,

77
00:04:20,439 --> 00:04:21,600
we will bring you

78
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:23,800
Xingguang City versus Shushan City.

79
00:04:26,959 --> 00:04:27,759
It's over.

80
00:04:29,480 --> 00:04:31,319
Zhong Jun has successfully proven

81
00:04:31,560 --> 00:04:32,360
that Shanhai City

82
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:34,319
isn't entirely full of losers.

83
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,399
Then I'm heading back to sleep.

84
00:04:36,680 --> 00:04:38,480
Been playing too much mahjong lately.

85
00:04:38,639 --> 00:04:40,040
Staying up late, haven't slept well.

86
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:41,360
You're not gonna scout the opponents anymore?

87
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:43,199
Old man An and that fool,

88
00:04:43,319 --> 00:04:44,519
what's there to watch?

89
00:04:47,199 --> 00:04:48,040
Then wait for me.

90
00:04:48,399 --> 00:04:49,079
Hold this.

91
00:04:49,639 --> 00:04:50,319
I'm leaving too.

92
00:04:58,279 --> 00:04:59,120
As everyone knows,

93
00:04:59,120 --> 00:05:00,920
Shushan City has always been a cultural hub.

94
00:05:01,040 --> 00:05:02,160
Of the ten top schools,

95
00:05:02,160 --> 00:05:03,720
six of them are in Shushan City.

96
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:04,360
That's right.

97
00:05:04,519 --> 00:05:06,920
Shu Qi has been famous in Shushan City for years.

98
00:05:06,920 --> 00:05:08,600
Serving as captain and starter this time,

99
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:10,759
he's sure to bring us something special.

100
00:05:10,759 --> 00:05:11,279
Indeed.

101
00:05:11,480 --> 00:05:13,160
Xingguang City is also a dark horse.

102
00:05:13,240 --> 00:05:14,439
Their captain, An Budong,

103
00:05:14,480 --> 00:05:15,839
is also starting in this match.

104
00:05:15,920 --> 00:05:17,480
Who will win this match?

105
00:05:17,480 --> 00:05:18,839
Let's wait and see.

106
00:05:22,720 --> 00:05:23,360
Please.

107
00:05:25,199 --> 00:05:26,000
Please.

108
00:05:28,279 --> 00:05:29,519
Fire.

109
00:05:31,399 --> 00:05:32,040
Li.

110
00:05:39,240 --> 00:05:39,879
Zhen,

111
00:05:41,079 --> 00:05:42,000
becomes thunder.

112
00:05:53,759 --> 00:05:55,319
Fire borrows the wind's force,

113
00:05:55,800 --> 00:05:57,279
spreading a thousand miles.

114
00:05:57,879 --> 00:05:59,439
Wild winds sweep across,

115
00:05:59,439 --> 00:06:01,240
flames raging on.

116
00:06:01,959 --> 00:06:03,560
Meeting water,

117
00:06:04,360 --> 00:06:05,199
they're extinguished.

118
00:06:18,480 --> 00:06:19,480
Thunder and fire collide!

119
00:06:19,480 --> 00:06:20,879
What a dazzling fight!

120
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:21,639
That's right.

121
00:06:21,800 --> 00:06:23,120
It's just spectacular!

122
00:06:36,519 --> 00:06:37,879
Perhaps this old man

123
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,439
will win unfairly today.

124
00:06:42,279 --> 00:06:43,399
What a pity

125
00:06:43,680 --> 00:06:46,120
the world will lose a kindred spirit.

126
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:48,800
Jiang Ziya.

127
00:06:50,199 --> 00:06:51,160
Thunder technique.

128
00:06:57,160 --> 00:06:58,800
Fuxi.

129
00:07:20,839 --> 00:07:21,920
Your Bagua

130
00:07:23,279 --> 00:07:24,319
is truly profound.

131
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:27,000
Balancing offense and defense,

132
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,199
advancing and retreating with measure.

133
00:07:30,800 --> 00:07:31,839
But both of us

134
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:34,759
have exhausted our immortal energy.

135
00:07:35,839 --> 00:07:36,519
How about

136
00:07:38,040 --> 00:07:39,600
we call it a draw?

137
00:07:40,199 --> 00:07:41,199
A draw?

138
00:07:43,279 --> 00:07:44,360
Why a draw?

139
00:07:45,879 --> 00:07:47,759
I don't think we're kindred spirits.

140
00:07:48,480 --> 00:07:50,040
While you were reading countless books,

141
00:07:50,600 --> 00:07:51,680
I was fighting.

142
00:07:52,800 --> 00:07:54,439
While you cultivated your temperament,

143
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,040
I was fighting.

144
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:59,160
While you were taking a beating...

145
00:08:03,680 --> 00:08:05,480
Your cane is made of iron!

146
00:08:06,079 --> 00:08:06,720
Stop!

147
00:08:09,000 --> 00:08:09,680
I lost.

148
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,319
I concede.

149
00:08:16,000 --> 00:08:16,759
I know.

150
00:08:17,279 --> 00:08:19,680
Your tailbone must really hurt right now, huh?

151
00:08:20,680 --> 00:08:22,279
Come on, come on.

152
00:08:22,480 --> 00:08:23,199
Let me help you up.

153
00:08:23,879 --> 00:08:24,519
Come on.

154
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:35,200
He actually escorted his opponent off stage himself.

155
00:08:35,639 --> 00:08:37,519
What a touching moment this is.

156
00:08:37,879 --> 00:08:38,480
Indeed.

157
00:08:38,600 --> 00:08:39,960
I believe if not for the competition,

158
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,720
they could've become great friends.

159
00:08:41,919 --> 00:08:42,720
Let's watch together

160
00:08:42,720 --> 00:08:44,279
An Budong's next performance.

161
00:08:45,039 --> 00:08:46,039
Next.

162
00:08:49,279 --> 00:08:50,679
I'm from Shushan City,

163
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,320
Bai.

164
00:08:55,039 --> 00:08:57,000
Looks like after the last match,

165
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:59,080
An Budong has lost patience for slow fights.

166
00:08:59,080 --> 00:08:59,679
Yes.

167
00:08:59,720 --> 00:09:01,480
Now he's going for speed.

168
00:09:02,159 --> 00:09:03,399
Are the people of Shushan City

169
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:06,080
all bookworms?

170
00:09:07,679 --> 00:09:09,240
My body's a bit weak.

171
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:11,159
I can't fight those young guys anymore.

172
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,279
I leave it to you.

173
00:09:14,559 --> 00:09:15,240
Got it.

174
00:09:17,799 --> 00:09:18,399
What?

175
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,159
Xingguang City is substituting!

176
00:09:20,480 --> 00:09:22,279
At the height of An Budong's fierce battle,

177
00:09:22,399 --> 00:09:24,320
Xingguang City actually chose to substitute.

178
00:09:37,600 --> 00:09:38,200
Yes!

179
00:09:38,440 --> 00:09:40,399
Yes, yes, yes!

180
00:09:40,519 --> 00:09:41,279
Xingguang City!

181
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,919
Xingguang City actually defeated

182
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:45,360
Shushan, one of the eight main cities!

183
00:09:45,360 --> 00:09:48,039
But Shushan City has always been a cultural sanctuary,

184
00:09:48,080 --> 00:09:50,000
so it's understandable they're not great at fighting.

185
00:09:50,320 --> 00:09:50,960
Exactly.

186
00:09:51,039 --> 00:09:52,480
Up next we bring you

187
00:09:52,600 --> 00:09:53,799
Tianshui City versus

188
00:09:53,799 --> 00:09:56,000
Yunhua City, one of the eight main cities.

189
00:10:14,279 --> 00:10:15,600
Tianshui City's Wu Qianqiu

190
00:10:15,600 --> 00:10:17,360
landed an elegant one-hit strike.

191
00:10:17,360 --> 00:10:17,840
Awesome!

192
00:10:17,919 --> 00:10:18,559
Yes.

193
00:10:18,559 --> 00:10:20,000
Wu Qianqiu, even in Tianshui City,

194
00:10:20,000 --> 00:10:21,919
is one of the standout fighters.

195
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:55,159
Tianshui City's Wu Qianqiu

196
00:10:55,159 --> 00:10:56,360
actually, single-handedly,

197
00:10:56,360 --> 00:10:58,320
tore through four Yunhua City players,

198
00:10:58,519 --> 00:11:00,559
even including their captain.

199
00:11:00,919 --> 00:11:03,120
Yunhua City is one of the eight main cities,

200
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,759
with heritage far surpassing Tianshui City.

201
00:11:05,080 --> 00:11:06,120
To put it bluntly,

202
00:11:06,159 --> 00:11:07,120
Tianshui City is smaller

203
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:08,639
than even a district of Yunhua City.

204
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:10,200
This is incredible!

205
00:11:10,399 --> 00:11:12,320
But Wu Qianqiu is also seriously injured.

206
00:11:12,399 --> 00:11:14,159
She'll probably step down, right?

207
00:11:14,159 --> 00:11:14,799
No.

208
00:11:14,840 --> 00:11:16,279
She chose to keep fighting.

209
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:18,840
She could have stepped down with honor,

210
00:11:18,919 --> 00:11:19,480
yet...

211
00:11:19,840 --> 00:11:21,039
I'm about to cry.

212
00:11:21,799 --> 00:11:22,679
Just forfeit. Yeah.

213
00:11:22,919 --> 00:11:24,720
Stepping down now isn't shameful.

214
00:11:24,919 --> 00:11:26,320
She still has four teammates.

215
00:11:26,679 --> 00:11:28,200
What on earth is she holding on for?

216
00:11:44,039 --> 00:11:44,840
Alright!

217
00:11:44,840 --> 00:11:46,720
Tianshui City's Wu Qianqiu

218
00:11:47,360 --> 00:11:48,000
is defeated!

219
00:11:48,600 --> 00:11:49,759
Coming up next

220
00:11:49,799 --> 00:11:51,679
is Tianshui City's second contestant.

221
00:11:51,799 --> 00:11:52,559
I forfeit.

222
00:11:53,120 --> 00:11:53,879
What?

223
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:56,080
He... he actually chose to forfeit!

224
00:11:56,679 --> 00:11:59,519
Your captain risked her life to wound him,

225
00:11:59,759 --> 00:12:01,720
yet he doesn't even have the guts to fight.

226
00:12:02,120 --> 00:12:03,279
Let's welcome Tianshui City's

227
00:12:03,279 --> 00:12:05,000
third contestant to the stage.

228
00:12:05,159 --> 00:12:05,879
I forfeit.

229
00:12:07,200 --> 00:12:09,240
Let's welcome Tianshui City's fourth member.

230
00:12:09,240 --> 00:12:09,919
I forfeit too.

231
00:12:09,919 --> 00:12:11,240
After Captain Wu Qianqiu,

232
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:12,480
three teammates in a row

233
00:12:12,480 --> 00:12:14,720
couldn't even beat one heavily wounded man.

234
00:12:15,279 --> 00:12:16,320
How pathetic.

235
00:12:16,480 --> 00:12:17,799
Let's welcome Tianshui City's

236
00:12:17,799 --> 00:12:19,320
fifth contestant to the stage.

237
00:12:19,320 --> 00:12:20,000
I forfeit. Can't beat him.

238
00:12:20,000 --> 00:12:21,000
What do you mean "can't beat him"?

239
00:12:21,279 --> 00:12:23,080
You don't even have the guts to try!

240
00:12:23,720 --> 00:12:24,879
Oh, Tianshui City...

241
00:12:26,720 --> 00:12:29,720
Congratulations to Yunhua City for advancing to the top four!

242
00:12:29,919 --> 00:12:31,080
But from this day on,

243
00:12:31,080 --> 00:12:33,440
I will always remember the name Wu Qianqiu.

244
00:12:33,519 --> 00:12:35,080
She's my idol for life.

245
00:12:35,159 --> 00:12:35,840
Indeed.

246
00:12:36,000 --> 00:12:38,279
Coming up next is Fengxue City...

247
00:12:45,200 --> 00:12:45,919
Xingguang City.

248
00:12:46,080 --> 00:12:46,840
Keep an eye on them.

249
00:12:49,919 --> 00:12:50,679
Forget it.

250
00:12:51,399 --> 00:12:52,159
Not important.

251
00:12:52,879 --> 00:12:54,320
No matter who wins in the end,

252
00:12:54,919 --> 00:12:56,240
they'll be crushed by Haotian.

253
00:12:57,360 --> 00:12:58,240
The Imperial Capital

254
00:12:58,720 --> 00:13:00,080
will surely take first place.

255
00:13:00,399 --> 00:13:01,120
You may go.

256
00:13:09,559 --> 00:13:10,240
San Gou,

257
00:13:11,000 --> 00:13:12,519
you've been visiting my brother

258
00:13:13,679 --> 00:13:14,919
quite often lately.

259
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,639
He tried to win me over before,

260
00:13:18,679 --> 00:13:19,679
asking me to spy on you,

261
00:13:21,240 --> 00:13:22,360
but I refused.

262
00:13:23,360 --> 00:13:24,120
Ever since then,

263
00:13:24,120 --> 00:13:25,519
he keeps summoning me over,

264
00:13:26,120 --> 00:13:27,480
trying to make you misunderstand me

265
00:13:29,519 --> 00:13:30,559
and drive a wedge between us.

266
00:13:31,240 --> 00:13:31,879
Don't worry.

267
00:13:32,240 --> 00:13:33,000
I'm not stupid.

268
00:13:33,600 --> 00:13:35,080
Go contact Wang Qiusheng.

269
00:13:35,919 --> 00:13:36,919
Some things

270
00:13:37,600 --> 00:13:38,720
need to begin now.

271
00:13:45,360 --> 00:13:46,360
I have a feeling

272
00:13:46,679 --> 00:13:47,879
he's hiding something from us,

273
00:13:48,679 --> 00:13:49,799
but I can't read him.

274
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:51,960
Whatever.

275
00:13:52,559 --> 00:13:53,720
In this world,

276
00:13:54,039 --> 00:13:56,120
everyone has their own secrets.

277
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,559
What we need to do

278
00:13:58,320 --> 00:14:00,039
isn't to dig up his secrets,

279
00:14:00,639 --> 00:14:01,759
but to let him

280
00:14:02,200 --> 00:14:03,639
take his secrets

281
00:14:04,159 --> 00:14:04,919
to the grave.

